<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.5.6">
<l>elliyum naṉpaka lumiruntē yēcilu mēcuka yēntiḻaiyār</l>
<l>nallara vartiṟam nāmaṟiyōm nāṇmaṭa maccana makkiṅkillai</l>
<l>vallaṉa collima kiḻvarēlum māmaṇi vaṇṇarai nāmmaṟavōm</l>
<l>kollaiva ḷariḷamul laipulku kuṟuṅkuṭik kēyeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if bejeweled ladies sit and slander [me] at night and full midday,</l>
<l rend="indent">let them slander!</l>
<l>We do not know the nature of those good women, [but] for me,</l>
<l rend="indent">there is no modesty, virtue, or timidity here.</l>
<l>Even if they get pleasure saying harsh things,</l>
<l rend="indent">we will not forget the dark sapphire-hued one.</l>
<l>Make sure you take me to Kuṟuṅkuṭi where fresh jasmine,</l>
<l rend="indent">which grows in the gardens, caresses.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
